    • 1. Project Description :
    • Workiy Academy serves as an innovative E-Learning platform catering to IT professionals and students, providing them with an opportunity to enhance their diverse IT knowledge. Interested candidates can easily navigate the platform to search for a plethora of courses tailored to meet their specific needs. The seamless interface allows users to register effortlessly for both online and offline classes, ensuring flexibility and accessibility in their pursuit of up skilling within the realm of Information Technology.
    • Roles & Responsibilities :
    • Create responsive and user-friendly interfaces using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript frameworks like React.js.Design and implement server-side logic, APIs, and databases using technologies such as Node.js
    • Develop and maintain databases, ensuring efficient data storage and retrieval.
    • Integrate front-end and back-end components to ensure seamless communication between the user interface and server-side applications. Work closely with UI/UX designers to implement visually appealing and user-centric designs.
    • Utilize version control systems such as Git to manage and track changes in the code base. Diagnose and troubleshoot issues reported by users or identified during testing.
    Project Details :
    Organization WORKIY - TECHNOLOGIES
    Client JEVITTY - (Canada)
    Team Size 7
    Role Full Stack Developer & Tosca Automation Tester
    • 2. Project Description :
    • Jevitty is a new way of looking at how we live in order to create an optimal balance of body and mind. Together we can transform what human longevity means, and help redefine your true potential. Through community, education and analysis, Jevitty is dedicated to unlocking the key to quality longevity for its users.
      • Roles & Responsibilities :
    • Developed, executed the automation scripts and analyzed the result using Tosca. Very Good Experience on Tosca Commander. Good work exposure on Exception Handling in Tosca.
    • Collaborated with the testing team to ensure the delivery of a reliable and bug-free product. Experienced in working on Web Hosting Management (WHM). Uploading Local Developed files into Server using Filezilla. Interacted with client on regular basis to clarify the questions.

      • CADDCAE Technologies | March 2022 - Nov 2021 (MERN Stack Developer & Trainer)

    • Work Description :
    • Managed and administered web hosting servers, ensuring smooth operations and resolving technical issues.
    • And also, I have been working as a MERN stack trainer at CADDCAE Technologies.
